title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 18 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 18 2022
description:
NHL testing data proves 100% vaccination won't stop covid. Lots of NHL players vaccinated, yet more than 70% have tested positive for covid this season. De Blasio won't run for New York governor. New Virginia Attorney General Jason Miyares joins Clay and Buck, talks about how the Youngkin team plans to reclaim Virginia from woke leftists. Fun covid quarantine fact: Buck broadcasts wearing a scarf from inside his apartment.
